{"type":null,"faqId":9738,"title":"P6S-U06  添加/取消闹钟","answer":"<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>a)</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点击</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">时钟</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">。再点击</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"> <img style=\"width:32px;height:31px;\" height=\"37\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30233\" width=\"32\" /></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">进入闹钟界面。<span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30232\" /></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span></span></span></span>&nbsp;</span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>a)</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30231\" /></span></span></span> </span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>b)</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">选&nbsp;&nbsp; b)选择<img style=\"width:24px;height:24px;\" height=\"35\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30237\" width=\"24\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">添加闹钟</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，进入设置闹钟界面，可以进行如下操作：</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>b)</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c)</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点击<b>时间</b>，设置闹钟铃响的时间。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>c)</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d)</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点击<b>重复</b>，选择需要闹钟重复的周期。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>d)</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; e)</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点击<b>铃声</b>，选择闹钟铃声。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>e)</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; f)</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">勾选<b>振动</b>，设置手机在闹钟铃响时振动。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>f)</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; g)</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点击<b>标签，</b>输入闹钟时间名称。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><span><span>g)</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; h)</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点击<b>完成</b>，完成闹钟的添加。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">在闹钟界面，可以看到当前所有闹钟的列表，去掉一条闹钟前面的勾选，就表示取消了这个闹钟。或长按一条闹钟记录，在弹出菜单中选择</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">“</span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">删除闹钟</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">删除您选择的闹钟。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"324","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396316458000,"seriesProductName":"P6 S-U00","visitedTimes":10,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}